      <title>今日は誰の夢を見る</title>
      <link>https://yuki9902-jp.github.io/posts/2015-04-08_%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E3%81%AF%E8%AA%B0%E3%81%AE%E5%A4%A2%E3%82%92%E8%A6%8B%E3%82%8B/</link>
